  "body": "Ejections are currently in \"per-block\". They should instead be in per-epoch.\r\n\r\nI argue per-epoch instead of per-slot because there is nothing during the middle of an epoch that lowers a validator's balance. Only after per-epoch rewards/penalties would a validator newly be below the `MIN_BALANCE` and qualify for ejection.",
